    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster protected by a professional ceramic coating, showing zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains completely smoke-free and pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is turn-key ready, boasting a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. There are no leaks, no odd noises, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that feels and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a folder of service records.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
