    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it to believe how clean it is! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
