    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in exceptional condition. This example is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical vulnerabilities have been addressed: the VANOS system has been overhauled with Besian components, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The suspension features a refreshed OE-plus setup with Bilstein dampers for neutralized body roll without compromising compliance. Bodywork is flawless, retaining original paint depth across all panels, while the interior leather shows zero bolster wear. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies this mechanically superlative vehicle.",
